---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components'
---
<section class="relative py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-24" id="email-services">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <div class="mb-12 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading">Professional Email Solutions</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        Elevate your business communication with reliable and secure email services using Zoho Mail.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="relative flex flex-col p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded shadow-xl hover:shadow-lg transition dark:border dark:border-slate-800">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Zoho Mail Free</h3>
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-primary mb-4">$0</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> 5GB storage per user</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> Up to 5 users</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> 25MB attachment limit</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> Web access</li>
        </ul>

      </div>
      <div class="relative flex flex-col p-6 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded shadow-xl hover:shadow-lg transition transform scale-105 border-2 border-blue-300">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Zoho Mail Premium</h3>
        <p class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">$1/user/month</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-200" /> 50GB storage per user</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-200" /> Multiple domains</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-200" /> 250MB attachment limit</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-200" /> Mobile and desktop apps</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-blue-200" /> Advanced spam protection</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="relative flex flex-col p-6 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded shadow-xl hover:shadow-lg transition dark:border dark:border-slate-800">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-4">Why Choose Zoho?</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> Reliable service</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> Strong spam filters</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> No website hosting lock-in</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> Modern technology</li>
          <li class="flex items-center"><Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-green-500" /> Avoid self-hosting risks</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Why Self-Hosting Emails Is Not Recommended</h3>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
        Self-hosting emails comes with significant risks and challenges, including:
      </p>
      <ul class="mt-4 space-y-2 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        <li class="flex items-center justify-center"><Icon name="tabler:alert-triangle" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-yellow-500" /> Lack of robust spam filtering</li>
        <li class="flex items-center justify-center"><Icon name="tabler:alert-triangle" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-yellow-500" /> Outdated technology and security risks</li>
        <li class="flex items-center justify-center"><Icon name="tabler:alert-triangle" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-yellow-500" /> High maintenance and management overhead</li>
        <li class="flex items-center justify-center"><Icon name="tabler:alert-triangle" class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 text-yellow-500" /> Potential deliverability issues</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
